<p>Cook County's northern suburbs are highly competitive for home service providers. Companies with branded fleets consistently report higher call volumes from neighborhoods where their vehicles are regularly seen. A single wrapped van driving through Arlington Heights, Buffalo Grove, and Palatine generates thousands of impressions daily at a fraction of digital advertising costs.</p>
